'''''Gift of Anguish''''' was a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Ro'ik chuun m'arh]]-class warship that was involved with the intercepting of the ''[[Nebula Chaser]]'' near [[Talfaglio]] some two years into the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. When [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Pollux]] lied about the presence of [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]] [[Alema Rar]] and [[Numa Rar]] aboard the ''Nebula Chaser'' to the Vong commander, the ''Gift of Anguish'' destroyed the vessel, killing all of the refugees aboard.

